<HEADLINE>
<P>
SHANGHAI, OPERA ACROBATS TO PERFORM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
The gymnastic stunts of the Shanghai Acrobats and the balletic displays of the 
Peking Opera Acrobats will be paired with the spectacle of the Imperial 
Warriors of the Peking Opera for one performance at 8 p.m. Saturday at the San 
Diego Sports Arena. 
</P>
<P>
This all-new program, based on traditions that date back for centuries, will 
include a re-creation of four popular martial arts sequences from the Peking 
Opera repertory. These excerpts will be fully staged and costumed with their 
original opulence. 
</P>
