<P>
Part A; Page 1; Column 1; Metro Desk 
</P>
</SECTION>
<LENGTH>
<P>
77 words 
</P>
</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
ORANGE COUNTY NEWSWATCH 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Tammerlin Drummond and Rick VanderKnyff 
</P>
</BYLINE>
