included teacher Candalario Mendoza, back row, far left, and future Justice 
Cruz Reynoso, middle row, fifth from right. ; Photo, Wilson school, above, was 
a collection of old Army barracks that cost $15,000; Lincoln school, below, was 
built with bricks and cost $75,000. Latinos went to Wilson, whites went to 
